<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1458788>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–6. Anisocyrta cvanachterbergi YaO, hOlOtype. 1. Lateral habitus, 2. DOrsal habitus, 3. Head (in anteriOr view), 4. Head and mandible (in dOrsal view), 5. Head and mesOscutum (in dOrsal view), 6. Head and mandible (in lateral view)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1458788/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1458792>
    dc:description "FIGURES 11–14. Anisocyrta xiaoliyaoae YaO, hOlOtype. 11. Lateral habitus, 12. Lateral head and mandible, 13. AnteriOr head, 14. DOrsal head." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1458792/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1458790>
    dc:description "FIGURES 7–10. Anisocyrta cvanachterbergi YaO, hOlOtype. 7. MesOsOma (in lateral view), 8. PrOpOdeum and metasOma (in dOrsal view), 9. Lateral habitus, 10. MetasOma (in lateral view)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1458790/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1458794>
    dc:description "FIGURES 15–19. Anisocyrta xiaoliyaoae YaO, hOlOtype. 15. Lateral mesOsOma, 16. Legs, 17. Lateral metasOma, 18. DOrsal head and mesOscutum, 19. DOrsal metasOma." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1458794/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

